        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Federal Police Camera and Accountability Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes requirements for federal law enforcement officers in uniform to wear body cameras and for federal law enforcement agencies to install video cameras in patrol cars.</p>]]></text>
